title: 550+ 3D Models (.3DS) w/ Textures
description:
All 550+ models contained herein are 100% royalty free, they can be used for any of your private/commercial endeavors. They were all harvested from http://archive3d.net (who annoyingly caps downloads to 30 models per day.)

For the sake of consistency, ALL models are in the *.3DS format. I have preserved the associated texture files with every model that supplied them. The unpacked size of the entire archive is about 2.2GB

I hand picked each of these models myself, for a project I am working on, so you won't find any garbage in this collection. I take no credit for their creation.
